洗樓<br />\n叫人地買煙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想做可以 pm 我"},{"pid":"91d4f2ae057f8c9f2de92a2d161faf7cb5c4eedf","tid":549113,"uid":67598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:41:32.000Z","msg":"之前做過綠色樽啤酒，其實呢行好少後生女做。同埋成日走黎走去，一日轉兩場，上場天水圍，下場可能係柴灣，仲要得半個鐘轉場。<br />\n同埋做啤酒妹經常性要做埋樓面,有次返酒吧叫我幫佢抹碗。加上唔會長返一個場，所以經常都同啲陌生人做「同事」<br />\n<br />\n利申：暑假可能會再做"},{"pid":"98d41cec531516277e89006dfd60cdac0e706cb6","tid":549113,"uid":165445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"526eb8f97c2607646f73219c30b02e1ec8b99e61","tid":549113,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb01db19f0ad6a38cbe8af2ebd8d3efed90927a4","tid":549113,"uid":165445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77cc06afff8c68e63d713b1885a42a726d45ab8c","tid":549113,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:56:43.000Z","msg":"笑死"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"好笑咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:33:29.000Z","msg":"係 諗起第時周街阿叔係你執邊可能陰陰嘴笑<br />\n細細聲同你講 條女服務係咪好好呢 識玩啊 師兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"咁的確人地嘅眼光係最難過嘅關係，睇嚟接唔接受到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe091d12ee14873f02253b20971a56b25dcc4c80","tid":549113,"uid":67598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2acb9fff545540ff91cf46466401d2063262198b","tid":549113,"uid":57505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"959c8d9c72131aef07b8180a16d681bc4a2a13c3","tid":549113,"uid":152253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1954755fe55b9cd5cbd5bf74d9cf308e1eb1ad","tid":549113,"uid":57505,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-05T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n間間啤妹都例牌著露臍，短裙，長 boot 架啦<br />\n不過條裙係裙褲<br />\n<br />\n有分酒吧啤妹，食肆啤妹<br />\n<br />\n做啤妹要好識撈<br />\n唔可以真係當自己淨係賣啤酒<br />\n<br />\n間酒吧/餐廳忙，要識得幫下手，落單收嘢乜都做啲，如果唔